## ✨ What is ResumAI?

**ResumAI** is an AI-powered resume analyzer that helps users check how well their resume performs for ATS-based screening.
It reviews resumes, generates smart feedback, detects missing skills, and gives improvement suggestions using **Groq AI**.

The platform is built with a modern full-stack architecture using **React, Node.js, Express, MongoDB, AWS S3, and Groq AI**.

---

## 🚀 Key Features

<table>
  <tr>
    <td width="50%">
      <h3>📤 Resume Upload</h3>
      <p>Upload resume files securely and store them using AWS S3.</p>
    </td>
    <td width="50%">
      <h3>🤖 AI Analysis</h3>
      <p>Analyze resumes using Groq AI and generate useful career feedback.</p>
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td width="50%">
      <h3>📊 ATS Insights</h3>
      <p>Get ATS-style feedback, score, strengths, and weaknesses.</p>
    </td>
    <td width="50%">
      <h3>🧠 Skill Gap Detection</h3>
      <p>Find missing skills and improvement areas for better job matching.</p>
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td width="50%">
      <h3>🔐 Authentication</h3>
      <p>Secure user login and signup using JWT-based authentication.</p>
    </td>
    <td width="50%">
      <h3>🌐 Production Ready</h3>
      <p>Frontend deployed on Vercel and backend deployed on Render.</p>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

