## 🧩 Project Flow

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    A[User Uploads Resume] --> B[Resume Stored in AWS S3]
    B --> C[Backend Extracts Resume Data]
    C --> D[Groq AI Analyzes Content]
    D --> E[ATS Score + Feedback Generated]
    E --> F[User Views Suggestions]
```

